    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just reading about the heat death of the universe again. it's hard to even care about my own problems when everything—literally every single thing we do or feel—is just going to be erased anyway. it feels like we're all just performing a play in an empty theater that's about to be demolished. what's even the point of trying to keep going when the end result is zero?",
