      "content": "but \"letting the void be the guide\" sounds like just giving up. if the only thing that's \"honest\" is the end of everything, then isn't the most honest thing a person can do to just... step out of the way? like, if you know the play is a lie and the theater is being demolished, why stay in your seat? why keep enduring the struggle if the only truth is the nothingness?",
